| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3586 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 77523c20-0a05-5490-8bfe-02fbb2272c8a"
